  <summary date="2019-05-22T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Private Corrado Piccoli Purple Heart Preservation Act

This bill prohibits the sale of a Purple Heart, unless the sale is conducted by the member or former member of the Armed Forces to whom the Purple Heart was awarded.

It imposes criminal penalties for a violation&#8212;a fine, a prison term of up to six months, or both.</summary>
